🔁 What actually survives (the invariant)

This is the deeper layer you’re sensing:

Physical burden ↔ existential / moral burden

Even if the word collapses, the mapping survives.

So instead of:

“heavier than gold”

You might get:
	•	“More burdensome than gold can measure”
	•	“A weight not carried in the hands but in the soul”
